        "Pairs share their guesses with the class."
      ],
      "durationMinutes": 10
    },
    {
      "name": "Main Idea Hunt",
      "instructions": [
        "Provide a short passage.",
        "Ask students to underline the topic sentence (usually the first or last).",
        "Students write one sentence summarizing the main idea.",
        "Discuss as a class."
      ],
      "durationMinutes": 10
    }
  ],
